---
source: tests/snapshots.rs
expression: diagnostics
---
- code: cognitive-complexity
  severity: warning
  message: "function `nested` has cognitive complexity 21 (threshold: 15)"
  primary:
    file: x.rs
    byte_range:
      start: 0
      end: 80
    line_start: 1
    col_start: 1
    line_end: 3
    col_end: 15
  notes:
    - score grows with nesting depth; flat code with the same number of branches scores much lower
  helps:
    - "extract helpers, return early, or invert conditions to reduce nesting"
